but trust me, I'm not.

198
00:08:28,216 --> 00:08:29,346
You'll see.

199
00:08:29,351 --> 00:08:31,361
(growly):
You'll all see.

200
00:08:31,355 --> 00:08:32,755
And Tiger Williams.

201
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:35,299
Your instructor
for Basic Pummeling

202
00:08:35,296 --> 00:08:36,526
and, time permitting,

203
00:08:36,533 --> 00:08:39,043
The American Novel:
1930 to the Present.

204
00:08:39,038 --> 00:08:40,008
(growls)

205
00:08:40,006 --> 00:08:43,146
As a goon, you have
one job on the ice:

206
00:08:43,146 --> 00:08:45,376
protect your team's best scorer.

207
00:08:45,383 --> 00:08:48,193
We call that person
your "primary."

208
00:08:48,189 --> 00:08:51,729
This is the most important
person in your life.

209
00:08:51,730 --> 00:08:54,100
Who's the best scorer
on your team, Muntz?

210
00:08:54,101 --> 00:08:57,441
- Bart Simpson.
- Then Bart Simpson
is your primary.

211
00:08:57,441 --> 00:08:59,341
Don't forget it.

212
00:08:59,344 --> 00:09:02,484
- Who do we protect?
- ALL: Our primary.

213
00:09:02,484 --> 00:09:04,664
And what do we do
for our primary?

214
00:09:04,656 --> 00:09:06,156
ALL:
Protect them.

215
00:09:06,158 --> 00:09:07,858
And who do we protect?

216
00:09:09,164 --> 00:09:10,504
Our primary?

217
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,240
This kid's good.

218
00:09:12,237 --> 00:09:14,637
