00:09:17,013 --> 00:09:19,823
♪ Hello out there,
we're on the air ♪

220
00:09:19,819 --> 00:09:21,519
♪ It's hockey night tonight ♪

221
00:09:21,523 --> 00:09:24,063
♪ Tension grows,
the whistle blows ♪

222
00:09:24,061 --> 00:09:26,231
♪ And the puck goes
down the ice ♪

223
00:09:26,232 --> 00:09:28,842
♪ The goalie jumps
and the players bump ♪

224
00:09:28,837 --> 00:09:31,077
