279
00:11:46,813 --> 00:11:48,753
Seriously, guess.
Guess!

280
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:51,860
- Please, just guess.
- Oh...

281
00:11:56,198 --> 00:12:00,038
Nelson, could I interest you
in a little skate?

282
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:03,149
(groans)
I could stretch my legs.

283
00:12:05,450 --> 00:12:06,620
(thudding)

284
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:09,320
Bart's my primary.
I protect my primary.

285
00:12:09,324 --> 00:12:12,974
What happened here
is a result of your actions.

286
00:12:17,173 --> 00:12:18,943
(scoreboard buzzes)

287
00:12:18,944 --> 00:12:21,854
Wow. Your kid's got real talent.

288
00:12:21,850 --> 00:12:23,950
No-game recognize game, yo.

289
00:12:23,954 --> 00:12:27,134
Shut up! Shut up, all of you!
Don't you see?

290
00:12:27,127 --> 00:12:29,497
There's nothing worse
than your kid being

291
00:12:29,498 --> 00:12:30,868
so amazing at something

292
00:12:30,868 --> 00:12:33,838
you can't blow it off!

293
00:12:34,642 --> 00:12:36,882
So, what's your old lady's

294
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,750
