416
00:18:14,054 --> 00:18:16,434
God bless back rooms.

417
00:18:17,695 --> 00:18:18,825
You know why you're here.

418
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:22,740
You borrow money from me,
I expect to be repaid.

419
00:18:22,738 --> 00:18:25,678
Time to make your bones.

420
00:18:25,677 --> 00:18:27,547
NELSON:
Lead.

421
00:18:28,817 --> 00:18:31,087
This is all I am.

422
00:18:31,088 --> 00:18:32,658
MOE:
Stop!

423
00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:36,730
Nelson, listen to me
