428
00:18:45,751 --> 00:18:47,721
Oh, not youse!

429
00:18:47,721 --> 00:18:49,121
You got to help me out.

430
00:18:49,124 --> 00:18:51,164
I only borrowed money
from the mafia

431
00:18:51,161 --> 00:18:53,471
