for teenagers

432
00:18:53,465 --> 00:18:55,665
so they could play
ten-and-under hockey.

433
00:18:55,671 --> 00:18:58,911
No one deserves a Kansas City
knee job more than this guy,

434
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:00,310
