435
00:19:00,313 --> 00:19:03,393
You swing that pipe,
that's your soul on the line.

436
00:19:03,385 --> 00:19:05,385
You're wasting your time,
"Coach."

437
00:19:05,389 --> 00:19:08,159
You said it yourself:
I'm just a fist.

438
00:19:08,162 --> 00:19:10,172
I know, and that's how
I saw youse at first.

439
00:19:10,166 --> 00:19:11,536
As a weapon.

440
00:19:11,536 --> 00:19:12,706
I was using you,

441
00:19:12,705 --> 00:19:15,505
