with beating King Toot here.

442
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:18,350
I knew it.
I'm in your head, bro.

443
00:19:18,349 --> 00:19:21,619
Feed him his own mustache!
No, wait. Don't, don't.

444
00:19:21,622 --> 00:19:23,532
Listen to me.
You're a great kid.

445
00:19:23,526 --> 00:19:27,196
You're determined, selfless,
a real teammate...

446
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:30,170
And you did for me
what I failed to do for you.

447
00:19:30,172 --> 00:19:32,912
You had my back, scuzz to scuzz.

448
00:19:35,650 --> 00:19:37,050
