you only see me as a knife.

451
00:19:41,294 --> 00:19:42,564
Did you know I got dreams?

452
00:19:42,564 --> 00:19:44,944
I want to open a gourmet
mac and cheese place

453
00:19:44,935 --> 00:19:46,435
called Louie's Gooey.

454
00:19:46,438 --> 00:19:48,778
And I'm learning Swedish
on a phone app.

455
00:19:48,777 --> 00:19:50,747
But I'm just a gun to you.

456
00:19:50,747 --> 00:19:53,947
Gentlemen, I don't
see you as weapons.

457
00:19:55,857 --> 00:19:57,757
(crying)

458
00:19:58,963 --> 00:20:01,573
Freaking millennials.

459
00:20:01,569 --> 00:20:05,179
Hockey's over, but maybe
we could still do stuff.

460
00:20:05,176 --> 00:20:08,116
You know, like
throw turtles at birds?

461
00:20:08,115 --> 00:20:09,845
Any time you want, kid.

462
00:20:09,852 --> 00:20:11,722
But whatever we do, from now on,

463
00:20:11,723 --> 00:20:14,703
let's leave
the violence behind, uh?

